{"tid":1471803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七公安出沒】疑似公安持棍扮示威者 七人小組微信群組傳情報","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:44:55.000Z","uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"653cf8f547cec7448d3c88d22b1e290d0c99bcde","tid":1471803,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:16:15.000Z","msg":"昨晚，一名來自深圳的男人，與其友人在機場形跡可疑，有指他影示威者大頭相。示威者上前詢問意圖和身分，初頭懷疑警察又再「扮演」示威者。一上前查詢，該名叫「徐錦煬」的男子與友人卻落荒而逃，現場留下雙截棍。後來示威者包圍徐錦煬對質，發現他與另外六人在微信群組不斷交流情報，七人在不機場不同位置「站崗」，監視示威者一舉一動。他們又在群組報料：「不要靠攏他們(示威者)，正追上來。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qrgiaPMDVPM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqrgiaPMDVPM&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3Xfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=22977c4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qrgiaPMDVPM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以後唔好再特登捉啦 根本捉唔哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n阻止有人做過火行為 冷靜處理就可以</span>"},{"pid":"d50211d4885ad3391ab30cc18309ad8e0beba55e","tid":1471803,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警配合中共國安特務(付國豪)做大龍鳳，<br />\n佢嘅任務就係<br />\n「鏡頭前展示俾示威者打到傷晒」，<br />\n國際記者影晒相，<br />\n用國際輿論同全國上下媒體大肆造謠，<br />\n指責示威者打記者/遊客，<br />\n跟住黑警先護送國安特務離開機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">條人渣絕對唔係記者！！！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4kdK7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4kdK7K.jpg&h=8672802c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdv9iuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkdv9iuk.jpg&h=da06f494&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}